{"data":[{"date":"23:15 20/08","title":"Klopp: \"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Neymar\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/klopp-liverpool-khong-bao-gio-chi-mot-so-tien-lon-mua-neymar.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Kop s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Neymar.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp tin r\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Neymar s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 2017, Neymar chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Barca \u0111\u1ebfn PSG v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3 PSG ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Mbappe t\u1eeb Monaco c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 180 tri\u1ec7u eurro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Jurgen-Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jurgen Klopp tin k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Neymar nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJurgen Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 222 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a Neymar s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro hay 200 ho\u1eb7c 300 tri\u1ec7u euro l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, khi Neymar gia nh\u1eadp PSG v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 222 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca chi 160 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Coutinho v\u00e0 105 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Ousmane Dembele\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Kylian Mbappe v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 180 tri\u1ec7u euro. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n suy ngh\u0129 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mua b\u00e1n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Neymar s\u1ebd s\u1edbm b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Kop s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Neymar.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp khang dinh Liverpool khong bao gio chi mot so tien lon mua Neymar\" title=\"Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/klopp-liverpool-khong-bao-gio-chi-mot-so-tien-lon-mua-neymar.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Virgil van Dijk, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Naby Keita, Fabinho, Alisson v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecf ra ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 200 tri\u1ec7u euro\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Liverpool c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSalah, Sadio Mane hay Robert Firmino, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 hay 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Liverpool s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2589","checkdouble":"194934"},{"date":"23:31 20/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nguoi-cu-chi-ra-yeu-to-giup-liverpool-co-the-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-mua-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jamie Redknapp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Liverpool d\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. The Kop ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, h\u1ecd k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Man City t\u1edbi 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jamie Redknapp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jamie Redknapp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/nguoi-cu-chi-ra-yeu-to-giup-liverpool-co-the-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-mua-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield \u0111\u00e3 mua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. The Kop \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Naby Keita, Alisson, Fabinho...V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Man xanh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Arsenal 2-1 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch th\u00ec Liverpool h\u1ea1 West Ham 4-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o, M.U thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f2n Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng HLV m\u1edbi th\u00ec Liverpool n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jamie Redknapp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wijnaldum khong roi Liverpool\" title=\"Wijnaldum kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/wi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jamie Redknapp tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA m\u00f9a n\u00e0y Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 Man City l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng Liverpool c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00e0 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 25 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Klopp s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch r\u00fat ng\u1eafn kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, Liverpool c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Stoke hay West Brom \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1ea1n m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng, b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 thu h\u1eb9p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u t\u1ed1t, Klopp c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i Pep \u0111\u00e3 xoay tua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn Klopp c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-2h-ngay-218-khang-dinh-suc-manh-172-194876.html\" target=\"_blank\">Crystal Palace vs Liverpool</span>, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2588","checkdouble":"194935"},{"date":"23:58 20/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Gabriel Jesus b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/nong-gabriel-jesus-bi-loai-khoi-dt-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro HLV Klopp s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p 2-4.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Croatia v\u1eabn tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Croatia v\u1eabn tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-tuc-dien-nguoi-voi-thong-tin-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 3 v\u00f2ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 g\u1eb7p West Ham.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, Lovren v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 9.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u00e1ng 8, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian Lovren kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u HLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Van Dijk v\u00e0 Joe Gomez \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham 4-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lovren c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6/9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i UEFA Nations League v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 th\u00e1ng 9.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-thong-bao-thoi-diem-lovren-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-172-194345.html\" target=\"_blank\">Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng </span>nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro HLV Klopp s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Lovren m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Klopp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Lovren ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Klopp v\u00e0 Liverpool s\u1ebd ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Khi m\u00e0 The Kop \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Lovren ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2587","checkdouble":"194936"},{"date":"00:27 21/08","title":"\"Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n\" chia tay Liverpool v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tham-hoa-thu-mon-chia-tay-liverpool-vao-cuoi-tuan-nay.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Loris Karius r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Besiktas \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Goal The Kop \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loris Karius mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Loris Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Simon Mignolet \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1 2018 bu\u1ed9c Liverpool ph\u1ea3i mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Loris Karius r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Besiktas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Loris Karius r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Besiktas h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Cuc-nong-Loris-Karius-roi-Liverpool-toi-Besiktas-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Karius mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Kop \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-karius-suyt-chut-nua-liverpool-da-khong-the-co-alisson-172-194927.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Karius</span>, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, thay v\u00ec \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Alisson th\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Karius c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Loris Karius th\u00ec Simon Mignolet c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch r\u1eddi Anfield, anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Serie A thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ra \u0111i, Liverpool s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 19 tu\u1ed5i, Kamil Grabara nh\u01b0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Karius s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Besiktas</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Loris Karius r\u1eddi Liverpool t\u1edbi Besiktas \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo Goal The Kop \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loris Karius doi dien tuong lai bat on sau man trinh dien te hai o chung ket Champions League.\" title=\"Loris Karius \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/day-ben-do-moi-cua-karius-neu-roi-liverpool.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Loris Karius s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n Besiktas \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n Karius 2 n\u0103m. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, Besiktas c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Besiktas s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o vi\u1ec7c m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Karius t\u1eeb Liverpool. Karius \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 49 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 19 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Premier Leage m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2586","checkdouble":"194937"},{"date":"00:36 21/08","title":"Victor Lindelof b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/victor-lindelof-bat-ngo-tho-lo-uoc-mo-khong-the-tin-duoc.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Victor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi, anh t\u1eebng th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Fabien Barthez, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Victor Lindelof t\u1eebng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Benfica v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2017. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Victor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Victor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/victor-lindelof-bat-ngo-tho-lo-uoc-mo-khong-the-tin-duoc.PNG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lindelof t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Lindelof c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tin t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Eric Bailly \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nVictor Lindelof mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi, anh t\u1eebng th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Fabien Barthez, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, khi c\u00f2n sinh s\u1ed1ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00f9ng qu\u00ea t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. T\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t khu ch\u1ee3 g\u1ea7n khu t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 b\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00fac b\u1ea5y gi\u1edd, m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 mua cho t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Fabien Barthez\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nBarthez \u0111\u1ebfn M.U n\u0103m 2000 t\u1eeb Monaco, trong h\u01a1n 3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf anh \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 139 l\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Alex Ferguson. Barthez t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u1edbi Marseille v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1993 v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1998 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U, Barthez c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i Old Trafford khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Tim Howard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nSau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2002/03, Barthez tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Marseille theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2003-04.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2585","checkdouble":"194938"},{"date":"01:02 21/08","title":"HLV Klopp t\u1ee9c \u0111i\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-tuc-dien-nguoi-voi-thong-tin-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro HLV Klopp s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia, phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua Ph\u00e1p 2-4.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Croatia v\u1eabn tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Croatia v\u1eabn tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-tuc-dien-nguoi-voi-thong-tin-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 3 v\u00f2ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam gi\u1edd. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0y \u1ea3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 g\u1eb7p West Ham.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, Lovren v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 9.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 d\u1ea1 d\u00e0y v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ecf \u1edf b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u00e1ng 8, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian Lovren kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u HLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Van Dijk v\u00e0 Joe Gomez \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham 4-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lovren c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 6/9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i UEFA Nations League v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 th\u00e1ng 9.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-thong-bao-thoi-diem-lovren-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-172-194345.html\" target=\"_blank\">Dejan Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng </span>nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro HLV Klopp s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Lovren m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Klopp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Lovren ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Klopp v\u00e0 Liverpool s\u1ebd ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n. Khi m\u00e0 The Kop \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Lovren ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2584","checkdouble":"194939"},{"date":"06:02 21/08","title":"Liverpool kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1, Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/liverpool-khoi-dau-nhu-mo-klopp-van-chua-mo-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool. \u00d4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Liverpool c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League hay kh\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Palace</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay (21/8) trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH, c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Man City v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau b\u1edfi thua k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Kop v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a James Milner v\u00e0 Sadio Mane v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Palace c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ch\u01b0a m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c. \u00d4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 1989/90.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u00e0nh th\u1eadt m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Liverpool c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 sau 2 tu\u1ea7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819-372-194933.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819-372-194933.html\">Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool: Si\u00eau Salah tinh qu\u00e1i, The Kop khoan kho\u00e1i</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n song Messi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018/18....</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita v\u00e0 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen, HLV Klopp c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u00fat nh\u00e1t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng ngo\u1ea1i. Keita c\u1ea7n c\u1edfi m\u1edf h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Mane. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau m\u1ebfn Keita nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian. Keita \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.\u201d<strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2583","checkdouble":"194940"},{"date":"06:25 21/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Man City b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/thu-mon-man-city-bat-ngo-dinh-chan-thuong-nang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng Man City v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea9y HLV Pep Guardiola v\u00e0o b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00f3c b\u00faa v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Ederson.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nClaudio Bravo \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e2n g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n Achilles trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ec9 ra Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Barcelona v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ki\u1ec3m tra chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Claudio-Bravo-dinh-chan-thuong-nang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Claudio Bravo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng qua trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Bravo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 tai n\u1ea1n m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Anh vi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng: \u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra. Cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng l\u00e0 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00fac kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0i to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Guardiola</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n Claudio Bravo ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 HLV Pep Guardiola. Trong tay \u00f4ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Ederson. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u00e1n Joe Hart cho Burnley v\u00e0 Angus Gunn cho Southampton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i, Daniel Grimshaw l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00fap tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Guardiola s\u1ebd \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong vi\u1ec7c xoay tua \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City m\u00e0 Guardiola \u0111ang \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, \u00f4ng t\u1eebng th\u1eb3ng tay g\u1ea1t Joe Hart ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Bravo t\u1eeb Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. 1 n\u0103m sau, Guardiola l\u1ea1i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00f3 Ederson t\u1eeb Benfica v\u00e0 Man City ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-dong-y-mourinho-man-city-khong-the-mua-dang-cap-172-194850.html\">Guardiola \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd Mourinho: Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim-172-194838.html\">Mourinho khinh b\u1ec9 Man City v\u00e0... \u0111\u00f2i ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1t-x\u00ea \u0111\u00f3ng phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/man-city-vs-huddersfield-ngoai-hang-anh-1982018-372-194821.html\">Man City 6-1 Huddersfield (KT): S\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Aguero l\u1eadp hattrick, Man xanh \u0111\u00e1nh tennis tr\u00ean Etihad</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-chui-tuc-vi-chan-thuong-cua-de-bruyne-172-194763.html\">HLV Klopp ch\u1eedi t\u1ee5c v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a De Bruyne</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2582","checkdouble":"194941"},{"date":"06:54 21/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-218-cua-doan-ttvn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao \u1edf ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/8 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c V\u0110V thu\u1ed9c \u0111o\u00e0n Th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ng\u00e0y 21/8, \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed9i dung. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh HCV v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a k\u00ecnh ng\u01b0 \u00c1nh Vi\u00ean, x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7 Ho\u00e0ng Xu\u00e2n Vinh hay v\u00f5 s\u1ef9 D\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00fay Vi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3 \u201cti\u1ec3u ti\u00ean c\u00e1\u201d \u00c1nh Vi\u00ean s\u1ebd ra qu\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng 400m h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p n\u1eef. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung \u00c1nh Vi\u00ean t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh HC\u0110 t\u1ea1i ASIAD H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u00f4 \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfc HCV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho b\u01a1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNgo\u00e0i \u00c1nh Vi\u00ean, \u0111o\u00e0n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u1eafn s\u00fang, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung 10m s\u00fang ng\u1eafn h\u01a1i nam khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tranh t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Olympic 2016 Ho\u00e0ng Xu\u00e2n Vinh. Ngo\u00e0i Xu\u00e2n Vinh, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 Tr\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c C\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, c\u00f4 g\u00e1i v\u00e0ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Thu\u00fd Vi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed9i dung th\u01b0\u01a1ng thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Thu\u00fd Vi \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a n\u1ed9i dung ki\u1ebfm thu\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, Thu\u00fd Vi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng trong s\u00e1ng nay. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Vi l\u00e0 Qu\u1ed1c Kh\u00e1nh v\u00e0 Kh\u1eafc \u0110\u1ea1t c\u0169ng tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung nam c\u00f4n.<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 218 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 218 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Lich-thi-dau-Asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-218-cua-doan-TTVN-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 218 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 218 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/ltd2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 218 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 218 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/ltd3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 ng\u00e0y 21/8 c\u1ee7a TTVN</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2581","checkdouble":"194942"},{"date":"06:54 21/08","title":"Thua tr\u1eadn, HLV Palace t\u1ed1 Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/thua-tran-hlv-palace-to-liverpool-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c James Milner th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sai l\u1ea7m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Palace</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Crystal Palace v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Michael Oliver x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Mamadou Sakho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Mohamed Salah trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly 11m, James Milner \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Liverpool. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2y, Palace kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Ph\u00fat 75, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Aaron Wan-Bissaka bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Salah ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Roy-Hodgson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Hodgson kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1 h\u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Liverpool kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gia t\u0103ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t. Ph\u00fat 90+3, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng, Salah ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palace.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Hodgson kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Roy Hodgson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn. \u00d4ng c\u00f2n cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00fang ra Palace c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0o ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi Max Meyer b\u1ecb c\u1ea3n l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n\u201d, Hodgson n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cSakho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng hay va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi ai c\u1ea3. Sau \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng James Milner ng\u00e3 l\u0103n ra khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng hay t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Max Meyer b\u1ecb Van Dijk ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-khoi-dau-nhu-mo-klopp-van-chua-mo-vo-dich-172-194940.html\">Liverpool kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1, Klopp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tham-hoa-thu-mon-chia-tay-liverpool-vao-cuoi-tuan-nay-172-194937.html\">Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n chia tay Liverpool v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-chi-ra-yeu-to-giup-liverpool-co-the-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-mua-nay-172-194935.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-liverpool-khong-bao-gio-chi-mot-so-tien-lon-mua-neymar-172-194934.html\">Klopp: Liverpool kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Neymar</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-vong-2-premier-league-201819-372-194933.html\">Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool: Si\u00eau Salah tinh qu\u00e1i, The Kop khoan kho\u00e1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-karius-suyt-chut-nua-liverpool-da-khong-the-co-alisson-172-194927.html\">V\u00ec Karius su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2580","checkdouble":"194943"},{"date":"15:52 20/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Malaysia vs U23 Bahrain 19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/u23-malaysia-vs-u23-bahrain-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 Bahrain: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Malaysia vs Olympic Bahrain b\u1ea3ng E Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 20/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Malaysia th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. Sau khi ki\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Kyrgyzstan \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Asiad, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1ea5m HCV \u1edf k\u1ef3 n\u0103m nay, U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 2-1. U23 Malaysia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 1 b\u00e0n thua trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00fap U23 Malaysia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu lu\u00f4n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bahrain ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ong Kim g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Bahrain gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Malaysia b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o. Khi \u0111\u00f3, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c song v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tay th\u00ec U23 Bahrain ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch 1/4 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Do ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam U23 Malaysia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o th\u00ec tin r\u1eb1ng U23 Bahrain s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2579","checkdouble":"194908"},{"date":"16:28 20/08","title":"Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andrew Robertson \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndrew Robertson chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Hull City \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Scotland \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Liverpool-muon-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Andrew-Robertson-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andrew Robertson \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Robertson \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Moreno \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y Robertson c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong c\u1ea3 vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/andrew-robertson-mon-hoi-cua-liverpool-172-183666.html\" target=\"_blank\">Robertson l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng PSG v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m Robertson, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Kop nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robertson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robertson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Robertson v\u1edbi Liverpool c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2021, song Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Scotland.\u00a0Hi\u1ec7n m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 25.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Robertson s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean 60.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robertson trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Kop thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Anfield v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng HLV Klopp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i West Ham 4-0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. \u0110\u00eam nay, The Kop s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2578","checkdouble":"194909"},{"date":"16:10 20/08","title":"B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1eafn anh v\u1edbi Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Liverpool h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Barca bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Firmino l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Firmino cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i qua c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. T\u00f4i \u0111ang mang tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn lao t\u1eeb NHM.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPremier League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb thu h\u00fat sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng cay \u0111\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nFirmino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf Liverpool hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho The Kop trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKhi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hoi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1ng cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn xa h\u01a1n th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 cho h\u1ecd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-2h-ngay-218-khang-dinh-suc-manh-172-194876.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Crystal Palace vs Liverpool (2h ng\u00e0y 21/8): Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2577","checkdouble":"194910"},{"date":"16:50 20/08","title":"Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Aaron Ramsey","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Ramsey \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ramsey. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ramsey.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ramsey, song m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, kh\u00fac m\u1eafc \u1edf m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Ramsey k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u00e0 Ramsey \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf Arsenal l\u00e0 110.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 250.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Arsenal ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 12 th\u00e1ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Ramsey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Tuong-lai-Ramsey-o-Arsenal-duoc-phong-len-hang-huyen-thoai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi, Ramsey c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c Arsenal ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ramsey</span>, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i. 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Ramsey r\u1ea5t gi\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Ramsey \u1edf l\u1ea1i, Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Ozil. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Ramsey \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Sanchez.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2576","checkdouble":"194911"},{"date":"16:50 20/08","title":"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/3-cau-thu-mu-xung-dang-bi-tram-khoi-doi-hinh-chinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. HLV Jose Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a MU l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Juan Mata\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3m kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3m kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/164704-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juan Mata kh\u00f4ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. \u0110\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng Mata r\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn Young kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Brighton c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1. Mata kh\u00f4ng k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Brighton v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y Young kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Solly March \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 tung c\u00fa t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cho Murray m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Mata c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t t\u00edch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng v\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Mata \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Mourinho thay ra ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Mata trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Eric Bailly\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bailly Lindelof\" title=\"Bailly Lindelof\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/4-cau-thu-choi-te-nhat-cua-mu-truoc-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bailly ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n khi\u1ebfn MU nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eric Bailly \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o MU. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Bailly r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brighton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBailly l\u00e0 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 khi\u1ebfn Man United ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu qu\u1ea3 penalty \u1edf ph\u00fat 43, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eeba c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 1-2. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i s\u1eeda sai b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBailly c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao cho Jones ho\u1eb7c Smalling, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Anthony Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial\" title=\"Anthony Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/164715-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial m\u1ea5t \u0111i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng khoan ph\u00e1 th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial ch\u01a1i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Sanchez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Brighton. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Lukaku trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Brighton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Martial t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Luke Shaw b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb Mourinho thay ra trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Martial m\u00f9a n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd g\u1eafn ch\u1eb7t tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1ed3n n\u00e9n v\u1edbi Mourinho, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Martial s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/2-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brighton-32-mu-172-194892.html\">2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-cau-thu-choi-te-nhat-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-172-194886.html\">4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2575","checkdouble":"194913"}]}